videos.title: Binocular glasses or modern glasses from Firmoo?
videos.description:
Did you know that Victorian binocular glasses, or â€binokle,â€ which we often associate with the elegance of that era, were actually quite uncomfortable? These glasses, with two lenses connected by a bridge that you pinched onto your nose, were a fashionable accessory of the 19th century. They looked stylish and intriguing, but wearing them for long periods was another storyâ€”they often left marks on the nose, and their weight caused noticeable pressure and discomfort.

As much as I love their vintage look and charm, I wanted something more practical for daily wear. So, I started searching for an alternative that combines style with comfort. Thatâ€™s when I found @firmoo.pl These glasses are just as chic but lightweight and comfortable enough to wear all day. 
And Iâ€™ve got a discount code for you on glasses - DM2940
@firmoo.pl
